Class Lawyer

  • java.lang.Object
    • Employee
      • Lawyer

  • public class Lawyer
extends Employee
    Class Layer is subclass of Employee. It implements one additional field, stockEarned that specifies the number of shares a lawyer has earned as a bonus. This class also contains getter and setter for stockEarned as well as a DVC and EVC. Also includes an override of the toString function to include lawyer-specific information and implements reportSalary() method to report salary and stock earned.
